@startuml Quiz Flow Sequence

participant Student
participant System
participant Database

Student -> System: Select Chapter & Level
System -> Database: Load Questions
Database --> System: Return Questions
System --> Student: Display Question

loop Until Level Complete
    Student -> System: Submit Answer
    System -> System: Validate Answer
    
    alt Correct Answer
        System -> Database: Award XP
        Database --> System: XP Updated
    else Wrong Answer
        System -> Database: Deduct Heart
        Database --> System: Hearts Updated
    end
    
    alt More Questions
        System --> Student: Next Question
    else Level Complete
        System -> Database: Save Progress
        Database --> System: Progress Saved
        System --> Student: Show Results
    end
end

Student -> System: View Progress
System -> Database: Get Progress Data
Database --> System: Return Progress
System --> Student: Display Progress

@enduml